high_descs: Turn around, then go straight, then turn right, then turn right again to face the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the apple on the counter, to the right the tomato.
Turn left, then go straight, then turn left, and go to the microwave.
Cook the apple in the microwave.
Turn to the right, toward the toaster.
Place the apple on the counter, to the left of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, take a right past the counter, and go to the counter to the right of the stove.
Pick up the apple from the counter.
Take the apple to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Take the hot apple to the counter with the toaster on it.
Set the hot apple on the edge of the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked apple on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, move around the counters to the right and head to the counter right of the stove.
Pick up the apple on the counter.
Turn around and bring the apple to the microwave.
Heat the apple in the microwave.
Turn right and bring the apple to the counter.
Put the apple on the counter in front of the toaster.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated apple on the counter.
